; npm authentication for publishing nirengi-ui-kit to the public registry.
; The real token is NEVER stored here — it is read from the NPM_TOKEN
; environment variable at publish time. Set it in your shell (e.g.
; `export NPM_TOKEN=npm_xxx`) or a gitignored .env, never in the repo.
//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
